{"tid":1483314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（818）（twitter召集）唔好再留係同溫層","createTime":"2019-08-18T11:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T09:59:14.000Z","uid":256966,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3b27989e69169827f2833f0807005982e75a53","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"今日好多相片，好多影片，終極和理非遊行，外國人需要知道，美國國會需要知道，大家去twitter推相片推post<br />\n仲有去名人／外國人twitter／外國媒體個度comment and upload今日的一兩張相片，俾大家知道今日有幾和平，香港人民意有幾清晰<br />\n<br />\n小弟twitter @lam_chau_bar<br />\n我都唔知可以做幾多，盡力做住先，利申我自己都係開了twitter一星期，唔係最識用<br />\n但係唔識用都同我用<br />\n三個月前邊有人識得be water 兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n全部都係靠trial and error咁試出黎<br />\n到而家係連世界都驚嘆我地的示威模式<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新玩既可以follow巴打 @masakibbb1<br />\n然後follow巴打d followers 全部係巴打黎<br />\n點玩呢?<br />\n1:search d tag<br />\n2: like同retweet<br />\n3:retweet係個心左邊個野<br />\nps retweet類似分享<br />\n當然你都可以自己出post<br />\n大家加油！！！<br />\n香港既social media都要革命！！！！"},{"pid":"eb8f410304628f9b2edd36d221754713569f2ec4","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQT3VSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQT3VSa.jpg&h=5347acc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fky0dDR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFky0dDR.jpg&h=d8079fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nheavy rain cannot stop us!<br />\nPeaceful, reasonable, non-violent protest in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nWhere there is no popo, there is no conflict.<br />\n#NoExtradictionToChina #ExtraditionBill  #HongKongFreedom #HongKongers #BoycottMulan <br />\n#Hongkongprotest #HongKongProtestors"},{"pid":"face20dc9c33e76e4092fdb1ac04474e1bbe212c","tid":1483314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 