ime":"2019-08-18T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04e84d49f2f672647a7c35ff838b3af55ee2fc7","tid":1483314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c819e1232b229ae602152bb7a7b8f86aba66942","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"twitter如果大家新開account<br />\n都可以花時間去add返戰友twitter<br />\n咁樣可以增加follower ＆ following的數目<br />\n睇落去唔係咁彊屍account／打手／水軍account<br />\n<br />\n新玩既可以follow @masakibbb1<br />\n然後follow返d followers 全部係巴打黎<br />\n<br />\n然後，唔好咁懶，加返張相做icon和封面相片。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a1576ace4e47c3830ffaf99e6d6401c2d6cf84","tid":1483314,"uid":996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n要對國際宣傳一定要用Twitter"},{"pid":"b87b7c003d9cbee56206aead1bf27935dbbfd5c3","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">新戰術</span></span><br />\n去常見的tag#HongKongFreedom #HongKongers <br />\n#BoycottMulan <br />\n#Hongkongprotest #HongKongProtestors #Hongkongprotests #AntiELAB<br />\n<strong><br />\n找出有哪些是外國人的post（例如：一些不是英文的文字、頭像是外國人&hellip;）<br />\n入去like，comment &quot;thank you for supporting us!&quot;，再加返今日818示威的和平相片，最後再follow對方。</strong><br />\n<br />\n務求令到外國人（而不是自己的戰友，因為戰友不是文宣對象呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）對香港示威更加有興趣和關注<br />\n<br />\n人性啲咁諗，對方係幾千公里以外，睇post同我地速度都一樣，一分鐘10個post都說不定，呢個時候有條友走入去講句多謝，令佢覺得有face，有價值，咁佢都會再有下次。<br />\n<br />\n利申：繼續諗緊點樣run twitter戰線，而家諗到咁多"},{"pid":"da6779d5819b043938b4198d5609526eeff4dc22","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n<br />\n外國人開始上網<br />\n好多美國人轉發緊twitter的野啦<br />\n<br />\n快d找人入黎做野"},{"pid":"6acfc486a16449afbe08db80458742dbbf352d37","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a6f67692fb02fdf9be4583e1c1349207275ed74e","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"快啲找人去twitter留言出圖say thank you做野啦<br />\n外國議員都岩岩係美國起身睇twitter share緊我地的818示威啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdHgxDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdHgxDL.png&h=8a1cf10c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9852007598b18421df1cdb05e17176da8a61560f","tid":1483314,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:15:19.000Z","msg":"屌 冇人推"},{"pid":"b8e8f64733260e75ed7ca03a6e6f90d7087a3931","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"要講人數的話，用呢條link，係英文內文的link<br />\n<br />\nMore than 1.7 million people turned out in Hong Kong, according to the protest organizer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-18/hong-kong-resets-democracy-push-with-peaceful-mass-march-in-rain?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;cmpid=socialflow-twitter-business&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=business\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-18%2Fhong-kong-resets-democracy-push-with-peaceful-mass-march-in-rain%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dsocialflow-organic%26cmpid%3Dsocialflow-twitter-business%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_content%3Dbusiness&d=xzf4O3tGv54ZmzQe4QccrP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=c90df0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-18/hong-kong-resets-democracy-push-with-peaceful-mass-march-in-rain?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;cmpid=socialflow-twitter-business&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=business</a>"},{"pid":"f5b5fc61c29f7e65c62663cc6e96ae2820bd31a0","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMyfOj3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMyfOj3.png&h=39f8732d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又有一個有成70k follower的twitter用家講緊818遊行啦<br />\n<br />\n我求下大家，p牌仔開唔到post，有無人幫手去開post叫人呢一刻用twitter！！！"},{"pid":"c6ed9731c699546849e0e910f9e6ee35cf547d4b","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n大家，在屋企的，唔洗再係屋企叫前線返黎，交俾前線叫人走<br />\n係屋企的搞好文宣，twitter開account，入去like and share"},{"pid":"bc8a7e9332f5b141e0584065ad65cf3dfefa2275","tid":1483314,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc82bd0a62755ace140c6c6c6477bb44e055b2c","tid":1483314,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb669abe6db891f7258d467586082ee773004702","tid":1483314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"649fc44e190661988b84b64f14368fc431395492","tid":1483314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"post已開<br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 有Twitter嘅幫手like &amp; retweet返818！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485320</a>"},{"pid":"d326b74eadb16eae29d47cccc5fde3f50dc0e41f","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"又有多個名人講今日的示威啦<br />\n連登人，唔好掛住互插，休息一下，去twitter世界做野之後再返黎連登啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾狗帶風向，一定有狗係連登想搞破壞<br />\n冷處理佢地的post啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rm5mJ9G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRm5mJ9G.png&h=9801b9e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64a6f289997b05ed1d35e84474acc9898967a729","tid":1483314,"uid":2533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"9b0b1f45fa070be4092821b1b36587f99bce272a","tid":1483314,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:49.000Z","msg":"如果個tweet本身有hashtag 我就咁retweet 有冇用？<br />\n<br />\n定係要retweet with comment另外留hashtag?"},{"pid":"ccaf71084f78db6c2691d1588154839c55c32d03","tid":1483314,"uid":263910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"follow me<br />\n@Wingggggz"},{"pid":"d4cfe13e70ddb4692546f46839d1560f64ca8483","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b0b1f45fa070be4092821b1b36587f99bce272a","tid":1483314,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:49.000Z","msg":"如果個tweet本身有hashtag 我就咁retweet 有冇用？<br />\n<br />\n定係要retweet with comment另外留hashtag?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"我無研究過<br />\n不過我個人傾向會用另一啲hashtag去retweet"},{"pid":"a6587d4f17de80fb053bdb8de7c718d816e9434e","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccaf71084f78db6c2691d1588154839c55c32d03","tid":1483314,"uid":263910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"follow me<br />\n@Wingggggz"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:18.000Z","msg":"已follow"},{"pid":"a9e4251156ba8f49e1b654a827e8c4765357a940","tid":1483314,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"由7點玩twitter玩到而家00：40<br />\n唔係好知道實時的香港發生緊咩事<br />\n但係見到twitter的戰略性<br />\ntwitter用家唔會好care香港示威的細節，但係會被圖片／video去吸引，去share。<br />\n<strong>特別係名人</strong>  佢地講完香港之後就講返自己國家的野<br />\n<br />\n1）like、comment and upload有代表性的818遊行相片－－最好對返準佢講的話題去回覆，不過都比較多係：<br />\nThank you for your support!<br />\n(8.18_HK_Protest) 1.7 million people participate in a peaceful, reasonable, non-violent protest in Hong Kong today!<br />\nEven heavy rain cannot stop us!<br />\n再加hashtag<br />\n<br />\n2）retweet （有時可以不用with comment，因為我地個twitter account無外國人朋友，retweet都係俾自己友睇only）<br />\n<br />\n3）找到外國人的retweet，最好係外國名人，其次係外國普通twitter用家（follower人數唔會有幾十k），再去like、comment<br />\n<br />\n今日用得最多的4張相（因為twitter只可以4張圖片一個post）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXk6aZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXk6aZk.jpg&h=44521853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upzraZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupzraZk.jpg&h=bd6d8f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J061Kjk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ061Kjk.jpg&h=f12f3825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8CDMxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8CDMxG.jpg&h=d90c9f80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c349242e8ca76bc6642b870fa2b997c92f4a36c3","tid":1483314,"uid":207259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:57:10.000Z","msg":"未訓 做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fec38017ade9acbc85545e53e5c1f174a7f8bf","tid":1483314,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:04:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b022415fe2426759020d1cb8890e319e1ccbada7","tid":1483314,"uid":71447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:13:51.000Z","msg":"其實我想講<br />\nTwitter個algorithm其實會好似Facebook咁<br />\n佢會不斷比你睇同你類似意見的Tweet<br />\n最終你亦都係會跌入番同溫層入面<br />\n所以希望大家無時無刻亦都要小心<br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n如果對著講中文的五毛Tweet就可以無視<br />\n唔洗駁斥<br />\n始終大家目標係英文日文等<br />\n無謂花精力係簡體五毛身上<br />